A road builder uprooted pipes, that is why you have not had water for a week, Nzoia Water Company Services has apologised to residents.The damage was so bad that it disrupted supply to schools, homes, hospitals, shops, hotels and other institutions in Bungoma town and Kanduyi, MD Patrick Munialo said on Friday.&lsquo;&rsquo;We ... are working round the clock to restore supply as soon as possible,&rsquo;&rsquo; he said. Munialo sought to allay fears of a shortage and water rationing.